cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to improve machine translation systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques to mine parallel data, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of embeddings and distance metrics suggests the possibility of the paper being categorized under cs.LG (Learning). The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of image captioning techniques, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
